name: stay malleable
description:
MAY YOU REMAIN ADAPTABLE IN THE FACE OF UNCERTAINTY

this is my wish for you in the last few months of 2021

the equilibrium symbol in the top right represents the constant balancing act

drawn with the deepest appreciation for the 600 minds, hearts and souls that have chosen to keep an eye on me

thank you
